            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"達利歐：市場一直在分散資產配置、減少對美國資產的依賴\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"672\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WRUNUHUQQ32ZseBb6gPafg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY3Mg--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-05/d54e0d60-2665-11f0-bff6-ed5916ded908\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">達利歐：市場一直在分散資產配置、減少對美國資產的依賴</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
