        {
            "title": "德國商業前景意外下滑 經濟缺乏動能",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Ifo Institute\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"562\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CPJoy_DyrMFON3WOcgKOUw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f806b6370cf945c8be421aaeb610f2cc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Ifo Institute</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 德國年初商業前景下滑，儘管政府承諾將進行大規模投資，但經濟依然疲軟。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Ifo institute周一發布的報告顯示，其預期指數意外從12月的89.7降至89.5。此前接受彭博調查的經濟學家普遍預測該指數將升至90.3。當前狀況指數則小幅上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Ifo總裁Clemens Fuest在聲明中表示，「德國經濟在新年伊始便缺乏動能。」製造業商業環境顯著改善，而服務業領域則持續惡化。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vLMKkVE6MTWFevCDCb35QQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/cef3caebbbc06c4ed24e465da561bd53\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這個歐洲最大經濟體在2025年實現了三年來首次成長，由此開啟了預計由政府基礎設施和國防支出驅動的初步復甦。儘管去年0.2%的成長率對總理弗里德里希·默茨而言仍「不儘人意」，但最新預測數據已顯現樂觀跡象。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5f67bef1-f055-3e7c-9e15-2cf30eb56f9d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">德國央行預測2026年經濟將持續回升，國際貨幣基金組織上周亦將該年度成長預期上調至1.1%。投資者信心同樣高漲，預期已達2021年中期以來最高水平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：德國經濟自2022年以來首年實現成長 受支出提振</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題German Business Outlook Unexpectedly Drops on Subdued Growth (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Kristian Siedenburg、Joel Rinneby、Harumi Ichikura、Steven Arons.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%95%86%E6%A5%AD%E5%89%8D%E6%99%AF%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E4%B8%8B%E6%BB%91-%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E7%BC%BA%E4%B9%8F%E5%8B%95%E8%83%BD-095006748.html",
